sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant OAuth as OAuth Provider
  participant API as Server
  participant DB as DB
  U->>OAuth: Sign in
  OAuth-->>API: callback code/state
  API->>OAuth: exchange code / get user info
  API->>DB: upsert user
  API-->>U: httpOnly session cookie
  U->>API: tRPC call with cookie
  API->>DB: load user and enforce role permissions
